{"tid":2511374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣漢光演習8日7夜電腦兵推日前結束 模擬共軍雙航母及兩棲攻擊艦南北夾擊台灣 飛彈及火箭炮襲擊台灣西部機場","createTime":"2021-05-01T00:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T01:05:30.000Z","uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"721e9ecf00d2e9e36baa72cd1addee8977546000","tid":2511374,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:42:51.000Z","msg":"國軍為期8天7夜的的「漢光37號演習」電腦兵推今天落幕，國防部強調，兵棋推演全程針對當面各項軍事威脅及敵武力犯台模式，均採「料敵從寬」的想定狀況務實推演，已達預期訓練目標<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n國軍漢光37號電腦兵棋推演23日開打後，從網路戰與戰力保存首先登場，接下來攻擊軍先以無人機騷擾，配合東風-15、東風-16等地對地導彈與衛士2型的長程火箭砲交叉運用攻擊機場、雷達站與各軍事目標；防衛軍現有的偵蒐系統可有效辨識無人機並予以反制，因此愛國者、天弓反飛彈防空系統仍可針對東風導彈進行有效攔截；<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但攻擊軍配合大量運用射程具有200、300與400公里的衛士2型長程火箭砲，長程火箭砲有效的圓周誤差率，確實讓西部軍用機場的跑道在損傷後，空軍機場人力與跑道搶救包已無法因應，而造成軍用機場被癱瘓。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據了解，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">防衛軍也發現不能讓衛士2型長程火箭砲部隊推進到東南沿岸海邊</span></span></strong>，若讓衛士2型長程火箭砲部隊進入福建沿岸位置，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">整個台灣西部大部分機場都在其射程範圍內</span></span></strong>&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n每一個空軍基地，都必須具備有一小時內，同時修復9個750磅炸藥造成的機場坑洞。<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但是在每小時來一波的長程火箭砲攻擊，確實可讓機場癱瘓</span></span></strong>。因此只要偵蒐系統發現長程火箭砲部隊往沿岸推進，掌握其部署位置後，在攻擊軍發動攻擊後，防衛軍則以機動的雄二E巡弋飛彈與制壓飛彈來反擊，不讓台灣西部進入其有效的射程範圍。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n至於東部的空軍花蓮與台東基地，在愛國者、弓三反飛彈防空系統與天兵防空系統建構成的防衛網，都能有效攔截來自東部外海航艦與巡弋飛彈的攻擊，保持戰機的升空迎戰<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3517094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3517094&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=2a5e6193\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3517094&h=835e08c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3517094</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=111768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D111768&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=bc9f15e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=111768</a>"},{"pid":"61031c673ef057255df1b2e5419c6e8cff3132ea","tid":2511374,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲都唔係新發現嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be8871ed25810ce4bb75f78e3713d5e08ca857f","tid":2511374,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6919c16b488c19e04ce6ed1015c7840b9bf9180b","tid":2511374,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"打未<br />\n<br />\n全世界做show"},{"pid":"1e76c150f4d99d8fc5da07f9e8e31da4856f2241","tid":2511374,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6919c16b488c19e04ce6ed1015c7840b9bf9180b","tid":2511374,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"打未<br />\n<br />\n全世界做show"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"死好多人，冇國家想"},{"pid":"5b6f45278ddcb91e2a97596fad90df355574ef87","tid":2511374,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 